OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy start, with
OL,6,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain moving
OL,7,Fsouthwards. However, soon brightening
OL,8,Fup during the morning with plenty of
OL,9,Fwarm sunshine developing for the
OL,10,Fafternoon. The northwesterly breeze
OL,11,Fslowly easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSunshine through the evening,
OL,14,Fwith plenty of clear skies overnight.
OL,15,FPerhaps a few mist patches forming as
OL,16,Fwinds fall light during the early
OL,17,Fhours. A cooler night than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
