OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FPlenty of sunshine through the
OL,6,Fday, once any morning shallow mist or
OL,7,Ffog patches clear. Feeling warmer for
OL,8,Fmany as winds remain light.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,11,FGenerally a cloudier day on Saturday,
OL,12,Fbut mostly dry with bright spells.
OL,13,FVariable cloud with sunshine at times
OL,14,Ffor Sunday and Monday. Temperatures
OL,15,Fgenerally above average, so feeling
OL,16,Fvery warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
